SDL2 files are from bitbucket.org/p_daniel/sdl-2-for-free-pascal-compiler.

To checkout the files:

git clone https://bitbucket.org/p_daniel/sdl-2-for-free-pascal-compiler.git temp
mv temp/SDL2 .
rm -r temp

Requires fpc and sdl2 to be installed.

Make should produce an executable named "main".

NOTE:
This sample currently does not work, see the following url for more info:
https://bitbucket.org/p_daniel/sdl-2-for-free-pascal-compiler/issue/3/runtime-error-207-at-b3d22754
